Name:           perl-Dancer-Session-Cookie
Version:	0.26
Release:	2%{?dist}
Summary:        Encrypted cookie-based session back-end for Dancer
License:        GPL+ or Artistic
Group:          Development/Libraries
URL:            http://search.cpan.org/dist/Dancer-Session-Cookie/
